- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possibility because the paper discusses the behavior of software actors, which are commonly used in distributed systems. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is a possibility because the paper deals with formal models of computation (the $\pi$ calculus and game semantics) and their relationship to each other.
